# Component Patterns for QR System

## Overview Page Structure

The main dashboard at [frontend/app/(app)/overview/page.tsx](mdc:frontend/app/(app)/overview/page.tsx) follows this pattern:

```typescript
export default function OverviewPage() {
  return (
    <div className="space-y-8 p-6">
      <QuickStats />        // Revenue, transactions, QR counts
      <QuickActions />      // Template usage, bulk generation
      <PopularTemplates />  // Most used payment templates
      <RecentActivity />    // Transaction history feed
    </div>
  );
}
```

## Template Component Pattern

Payment templates should follow this structure:

```typescript
interface TemplateCardProps {
  template: PaymentTemplate;
  onGenerateQR: (template: PaymentTemplate) => void;
}

function TemplateCard({ template, onGenerateQR }: TemplateCardProps) {
  return (
    <Card className="group hover:shadow-md transition-shadow cursor-pointer">
      <CardHeader>
        <div className="flex items-center space-x-3">
          <div className={`w-10 h-10 ${template.color} rounded-lg`}>
            {template.icon}
          </div>
          <CardTitle>{template.name}</CardTitle>
          <Badge>{template.usageCount}x used</Badge>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>€{template.amount}</p>
        <Button onClick={() => onGenerateQR(template)}>
          Generate QR
        </Button>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}
```

## QR Generation Component

```typescript
interface QRDisplayProps {
  transaction: GeneratedTransaction;
  isLoading: boolean;
}

function QRDisplay({ transaction, isLoading }: QRDisplayProps) {
  if (isLoading) {
    return <LoadingSpinner>Generating QR...</LoadingSpinner>;
  }

  return (
    <div className="text-center space-y-4">
      <QRCode value={transaction.qrData} size={300} />
      <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold">€{transaction.amount}</h2>
      <p className="text-muted-foreground">{transaction.templateName}</p>
      <p className="text-sm">Variable Symbol: {transaction.variableSymbol}</p>
      <div className="flex gap-2">
        <Button>Download</Button>
        <Button variant="outline">Generate New</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

## Analytics Components

Stats components in [frontend/app/(app)/overview/components/](mdc:frontend/app/(app)/overview/components/) should show:

- **Quick Stats**: Revenue, transaction count, QR generations, active users
- **Recent Activity**: Latest QR generations with status indicators
- **Template Performance**: Usage counts and revenue per template

## UI Component Imports

Use consistent imports from [frontend/components/ui/](mdc:frontend/components/ui):

```typescript
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '~/components/ui/card';
import { Button } from '~/components/ui/button';
import { Badge } from '~/components/ui/badge';
```

All components should follow shadcn/ui patterns with proper TypeScript interfaces and responsive design.
